tatus\", params \u003d {\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u0027status\u0027 : overallStatus})\n\t\t\telse:\n\t\t\t\tutils.messages.errors.showErrorMessage(\"File empty, please upload file with at least 1 row containing a device\")\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\telse:\n\t\t\tutils.messages.errors.showErrorMessage(\"File empty, please upload file with at least 1 row containing a device\")\n\texcept Exception as e:\n\t\tsystem.perspective.print(e)\n\t\tutils.messages.errors.showErrorMessage(\"Error processing bulk upload: \" + str(e))\n\t"
